<font size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Yto yto.
<br>
<br>
Today we killed Dragons, and a bunch of them too. We had a really late start, and amazingly managed to die to Eashen of the Sky again. Our excuse was that we only had 27 people on, but so what? Nah, actually, it was a flawless fight until our maintanks defensive ran out and died. The second tank was LD at this stage and the third and last warrior died faster than Kolienu can loot. This, ofcourse, cannot be good. He had to go.
<br>
<br>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Eashen.jpg>
<br>
<br>
Loot was  a Twisted Bastard Steel Sword for <b>Fatal</b> and Twisted Steel Gauntlets that went to <b>Leandred</b>. After the kill we were gonna pull Aaryonar's pets, but things wasnt going our way... He came also. After a slow CR, we tried again, and once again, he came. Ok, enough on that... We had several people logging, it was past midnight. We CoH'd up to backdragons and did them in a slightly unusual order. Jorlleag, Zlexak, Sevalak, Cekenar and Lady Nevederia. Here's your killshots to prove we arent lying Euro trash.
<br>
<br>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Jorlleag.jpg>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Zlexak.jpg>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Sevalak.jpg>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Cekenar.jpg>
<img src=http://home.worldonline.dk/~kingri/Nevederia.jpg>
<br>
<br>
Loot was phat, <b>Balgoth</b> got a Sprinkler of the Spirits, <b>Moonwalker</b> got a Facesmasher, <b>Chwing</b> and <b>Lowi</b> both got a Nevederia's Claw, <b>Jmich</b> got a Dragon Skin Bracelet, <b>Lowi</b> got a Axe of Resistance, <b>Leandred</b> got a Shield of the Dawn, <b>Polish</b> got a Silver Dagger of Destruction, <b>Rinderwahn</b> got a Mithril Helm, <b>Vipsindsyg</b> got Mithril Boots, <b>Zahlia</b> got a Shawl of Perception, <b>Bayla</b> got a Siren Song, Dagger of the Sea, <b>Rtyui</b> got a Bracelet of the Deep Sea and lastly, <b>Armonegonx</b> got a Shield of Thorns and <b>Sick</b> got a Shield of Dragonkind.
<br>
<br>
Wow, what a load of phat loots we have gotten in the last few days. Time to call it a night here, patch tomorrow again, so more dragons are gonna die!
<br>
<br>
Ok, now for a rant, why do the Velious chars look so gay? Just look at this, the Erudite male is seriously screwed up!!
<br>
<br>
<img src=http://members.shaw.ca/sterne/pic/bala7.JPG>
<br>
Bah, I'm keeping my Luclin graphics off =)
